@startuml High_Level_Parkinson_Prediction_Flow
title Parkinson's Disease Prediction System - High-Level Flow\n(User Journey + Algorithm Architecture Overview)

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontColor black
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor white
skinparam ActivityBorderColor black
skinparam PartitionBorderColor black
skinparam PartitionBackgroundColor #F8F9FA

||**USER LAYER**|
start
:User Login/Register;
:Select Input Type;
note right
  • Audio (speech)
  • Image (handwriting)  
  • Video (gait)
  • Combined video
end note

||**INPUT PROCESSING**|
if (Input provided?) then (File Upload)
  :Upload & Validate File;
  :Extract Features;
  note right
    **Feature Extraction:**
    • Speech → 22 acoustic features
    • Handwriting → 10 motor features
    • Gait → 10 movement features
  end note
else (Manual Input)
  :Enter Feature Values;
endif

:Prepare Model Input;
note right
  **Input Preparation:**
  • Scale features
  • Handle missing modalities (zero-fill)
  • Always 3 vectors: [22], [10], [10]
end note

||**AI MODEL PROCESSING**|

:**Step 1: Parallel Encoding**;
fork
  :Speech Encoder\n(SE-ResNet 1D);
  :22 features → 64D embedding;
fork again
  :Handwriting Encoder\n(SE-ResNet 1D);
  :10 features → 64D embedding;
fork again
  :Gait Encoder\n(SE-ResNet 1D);
  :10 features → 64D embedding;
end fork

:**Step 2: Attention Fusion**;
:Score each modality importance;
:Compute attention weights;
:Fuse embeddings → Single 64D vector;
note right
  **Attention Mechanism:**
  • Learns which modality to trust most
  • Example: [Speech: 55%, Hand: 15%, Gait: 30%]
  • Handles missing data automatically
end note

:**Step 3: Classification**;
:Dense layers (64→32→1);
:Apply Sigmoid;
:Generate probability & prediction;

||**OUTPUT PROCESSING**|
:Format Results;
note right
  **Output:**
  • Prediction: Parkinson's/Healthy
  • Confidence: 0-100%
  • Attention weights
  • Feature importance
end note

:Save to Database;
:Return JSON Response;

||**USER INTERFACE**|
:Display Results;
:Show Explanation;
:Visualize Attention Weights;

:User Reviews Results;
:Option for New Prediction;

stop

note bottom
  **Key System Features:**
  ✓ Multimodal AI (speech + handwriting + gait)
  ✓ Flexible input (1, 2, or 3 modalities)
  ✓ Explainable AI with attention visualization
  ✓ Real-time processing from raw files
  ✓ Clinical-grade accuracy and reliability
end note

@enduml